# Advanced Student Management System

## Objective
This project is designed to implement a comprehensive *Student Management System* using *Advanced Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)* principles in Java. It supports full CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete), persistent file storage, input validation, and utilizes efficient Java Collections for data handling.

## Features
- Add, remove, update, search students
- Display all students (sorted by ID or name)
- Save/load data using students.dat
- Uses ArrayList, HashMap, TreeSet
- Input validation and exception handling

## How to Run
1. Compile:
   javac Student.java StudentManager.java Main.java
2. Run:
   java Main

## Files Included
- Student.java
- StudentManager.java
- Main.java
- students.dat (generated)
- README.txt
